# Admin Dashboard

This folder contains the administrative dashboard pages for Printokids PH.

## Main Files

- `admin_index.html` - Main admin dashboard layout with tabs for Dashboard, Products, Inventory, Orders, Event Bookings, and Users.
- `admin_dashboard.js` - Handles admin dashboard logic, API requests, tab switching, CRUD actions, filtering, searching, exporting, and dashboard summaries.
- `admin_styles.css` - Contains custom styling for the admin dashboard.
- `images/` - Contains admin dashboard image assets.

## Admin Dashboard Modules

### Dashboard
Displays an overview of the system, including total products, low stock items, product orders, event bookings, registered users, low stock alerts, recent product orders, and recent event bookings.

### Products
Displays the product catalog available for client ordering. This is mainly for viewing/searching/filtering/exporting product catalog data.

### Inventory
Used for product inventory management. Admin can add products to inventory, edit stock details, delete products, manage current stock, reorder level, and stock status.

### Orders
Displays product orders only. Product orders come from client cart checkout and are stored in `product_orders` and `product_order_items`.

### Event Bookings
Displays event service bookings only. Event bookings come from event service booking data and are stored in `event_orders` and `order_services`.

### Users
Displays registered customer accounts. Users are created through client registration. Admin can edit or delete user records when needed.

## Related API Files

The admin dashboard connects to backend PHP APIs located in the `/api` folder:

- `inventory.php`
- `product_orders.php`
- `event_bookings.php`
- `customers.php`

## Rule

Do not place customer-facing pages in this folder. Client-facing pages should stay inside the `/client` folder.
